<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٥٤٢ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ , عَنْ قَتَادَةَ ,<span class="c5"> فِي قَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{وَجَعَلْنَا جَهَنَّمَ لِلْكَافِرِينَ حَصِيرًا}</span> <span class="c4">[الإسراء: ٨]</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> مُحِبٌّ: <span class="c2">«حُصِرُوا فِيهَا»</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ الْحَسَنُ:</span> <span class="c2">«حَصِيرًا فِرَاشًا مِهَادًا»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>